[media] media: Add a driver for the ov5645 camera sensor

The ov5645 sensor from Omnivision supports up to 2592x1944
and CSI2 interface.

The driver adds support for the following modes:
- 1280x960
- 1920x1080
- 2592x1944

Output format is packed 8bit UYVY.

